# TypeFlow Marketplace Preview Placeholder

This file is a placeholder for the marketplace preview image.

## Requirements
- Format: PNG
- Recommended size: 1200x630 pixels (standard marketplace preview)
- Should showcase the plugin UI and key features

## Suggested Content
- Screenshot of the TypeFlow plugin interface
- Highlight key features:
  - Font scanning panel
  - Font selector with search
  - Size controls (font size, line height, letter spacing)
  - Preview toggle
  - Apply button
- Include the TypeFlow logo/branding
- Add descriptive text overlay highlighting main features

## To Replace
Replace this placeholder with an actual preview.png file in the same directory.
This image will be displayed in the Framer plugin marketplace.
